<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的生肖<delay8 />是鼠～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就是今年的主角～<delay20 />
想想<delay20 />都有点不好意思了呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要用我这一对大耳朵，<delay20 />
把大家对我的评价，<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一字不差地听清楚～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道<delay8 />今年是什么年吗～？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻～<delay8 />今年呀<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是牛年！<delay20 />我的生肖年哦～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但话说回来，<delay8 />我还是我，<delay20 />
没有任何变化哦～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要今年也能<delay8 />开心度过就够了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />今年是虎年，<delay20 />我的生肖年～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的目标就是成为<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以让大家依靠的首领～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要像我的妈妈一样，<delay8 />
做到微笑着、点着头，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />倾听大家的话语～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我引以为豪的长耳朵，<delay20 />
今年要更加<delay8 />
用心地打理才是～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为，<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年是兔年啊～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家一定会<delay8 />
特别关注我的呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我刚刚<delay8 />才反应过来，<delay20 />
今年是马年啊～？<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么办～<delay frames="40" />
忽然开始紧张起来了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还是赶快逃走吧～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">今年的生肖是<delay8 />羊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是我！对不对～？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的我<delay8 />一定人气十足！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家<delay8 />会不会都来看我呀？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay20 />要是藏在被毛里的点心被发现了，<delay8 />
那该怎么办啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />12年一轮，<delay8 />今年终于轮到猴年了！<delay frames="40" />
我高兴得<delay8 />恨不得马上去爬一爬树呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />不过，<delay8 />要小心不要一兴奋
从树上摔下来了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不然就浪费了这愉悦的心情啦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你知道<delay8 />今年是什么年吗～？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />提示就是我～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻～<delay20 />正确答案是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />鸡年！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要挥动<delay8 />我引以为傲的羽翅，<delay20 />
在<tag a="110" b="33" />上飞翔，<delay8 />
并为大家送去幸福之风～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年终于到狗年了～！<delay frames="40" />
12年轮一次，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我终于等到了呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年我会更努力地<delay8 />
摇动我的尾巴的～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我预感，今年于我来说，<delay20 />
会是非常棒的一年～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，<delay20 />我引以为傲的尾巴<delay20 />
比以往更加卷翘了呢！<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让人感觉很高兴呢～!<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>